{"tid":2297717,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"用私伙對講機涉違《警察通例》 警方回覆相關警員已被「提醒及訓示」","createTime":"2020-11-23T13:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T16:02:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4c2da0c8c159ea432768ddad84681dc00b4f1583","tid":2297717,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:01:10.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》上月踢爆有警員在執行職務期間，使用在大陸購物網站淘寶及鴨寮街有售、沒有錄音功能的「私伙」無線電對講機，警方當時並無正面回應，僅指會了解事件，事隔一個月，警方回覆指已就相關法規提醒及「訓示」相關人員，但無回應使用「私伙」對講機的警員人數、採購程序、以及使用時的對話是否有紀錄等問題。<br />\n<br />\n報道刊出後一個月，警方回應指已了解及調查事件，就有關法規提醒及訓示相關人員必須使用警隊提供的通訊設備，以確保符合行動及保安要求，並無回應使用「私伙」對講機的警員人數、採購程序、使用時的對話是否有紀錄等問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/5K4YR6FGK5FE5EJYYSCTICPMVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2F5K4YR6FGK5FE5EJYYSCTICPMVM%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnQFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=c89a4a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2F5K4YR6FGK5FE5EJYYSCTICPMVM%2F&h=0bb54058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/5K4YR6FGK5FE5EJYYSCTICPMVM/</a>"},{"pid":"ce1c6ae635304d592a061071a74b4368bcee69af","tid":2297717,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959dc1eacb5d6df953010272fef4c800f128f029","tid":2297717,"uid":11291,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:02:08.000Z","msg":"訓示了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97d1e9787d58fa743bc148fb93d5b16f8902fe9","tid":2297717,"uid":22556,"like":10,"dislike":